sentences.sentence: Our results suggest GH2 acts as a primarily multifunctional CAD to synthesize coniferyl.

sentences.sentence: Multifunctional production department is a very noisy place.

sentences.sentence: VigilX also supports standard cockpit multifunctional displays (MFD) or head-up displays (HUD).
sentences.translation: VigilX还支持标准驾驶舱的多功能显示器(MFD)或仰视显示器(HUD)。
